snippet.title: Ztar Attack 2: A Blast to the Past - Download Video (v1.0b)
snippet.description:
The second installement of the Ztar Attack series is finally here! With 90 Time Stars and linear levels, this game marks a huge change of pace from the first episode. Prepare yourself to get back in time in order to save the Mushroom Kingdom!

I especially want to thank aglab2 for his help, his tips were precious during these 9 months of development!
